<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>nothypridle — Third-Party Licenses</title>
<style>
  body { font-family: system-ui, sans-serif; max-width: 80ch; margin: 2em auto; padding: 0 1em; line-height: 1.5; color: #1a1a1a; }
  h1 { border-bottom: 1px solid #ccc; padding-bottom: .3em; }
  h2 { margin-top: 2.5em; }
  h3 { font-family: monospace; margin: 2em 0 .5em; }
  hr { border: none; border-top: 1px solid #ddd; margin: 2em 0; }
  pre { background: #f4f4f4; padding: 1em; overflow-x: auto; white-space: pre-wrap; font-size: .85em; border-radius: 4px; }
  .crate-name { font-weight: 700; }
  .crate-meta { color: #555; font-size: .9em; }
  ul { padding-left: 1.2em; }
  li { margin: .2em 0; }
</style>
</head>
<body>
<h1>nothypridle — Third-Party Notices &amp; Licenses</h1>

<p>
  Copyright &copy; 2026 Nikita Goncharov &lt;ininids@ininids.in.rs&gt;<br>
  Licensed under <strong>BSD-3-Clause</strong> —
  <a href="https://github.com/ininids/nothypridle">https://github.com/ininids/nothypridle</a>
</p>

<p>
  This product includes the following third-party Rust crates. Each section reproduces
  the full license text under which the listed crates are distributed, as declared in
  their respective <code>Cargo.toml</code> metadata.
</p>

<hr>

{{#each licenses}}
  {{#if first_of_kind}}
<h2>{{name}} ({{id}})</h2>
  {{/if}}
  {{#each used_by}}
<h3>{{#if crate.repository}}<a href="{{crate.repository}}">{{crate.name}} v{{crate.version}}</a>{{else}}{{crate.name}} v{{crate.version}}{{/if}}</h3>
<p class="crate-meta">
  {{#if crate.authors}}Copyright &copy; {{#each crate.authors}}{{this}}{{#unless @last}}, {{/unless}}{{/each}}<br>{{/if}}
  License: {{crate.license}}
</p>
<pre>{{../text}}</pre>
  {{/each}}
{{/each}}
</body>
</html>
